      <akn:section eId="sec_28:8_303">
        <akn:num>28:8-303</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Protected purchaser.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_28:8-303_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>For the purposes of this article, the term “protected purchaser” means a purchaser of a certificated or uncertificated security, or of an interest therein, who:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_28:8-303_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In addition to acquiring the rights of a purchaser, a protected purchaser also acquires its interest in the security free of any adverse claim.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
